criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  having a score, at baseline, on the Generalised Anxiety Disorder 7 (GAD-7) scale of
             between 8 and 15, inclusive;

          -  having regular internet access;

          -  being based in the UK.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  significant risk issues in the last year;

          -  currently receiving another psychological intervention, whether it be self-help or
             face-to-face;

          -  having recently (within the last six months) completed a psychological intervention.
